item.title: CVE-2020-13575|2024-08-04T12:25:16.113Z -- genivia -- gsoap
item.description: A denial-of-service vulnerability exists in the WS-Addressing plugin functionality of Genivia gSOAP 2.8.107. A specially crafted SOAP request can lead to denial of service. An attacker can send an HTTP request to trigger this vulnerability.
